    public static class FullTextIndex.SearchHit

    This is the output record for our search procedure. All procedures that return results return them as a Stream of Records, where the records are defined like this one - customized to fit what the procedure is returning.

    These classes can only have public non-final fields, and the fields must be one of the following types:

    • String
    • Long or long
    • Double or double
    • Number
    • Boolean or boolean
    • Node
    • Relationship
    • Path
    • Map with key String and value Object
    • List of elements of any valid field type, including List
    • Object, meaning any of the valid field types
